		"txt":"[{\"proGood\":\"Convenient Expansion\",\"proName\":\"It can add or delete the back-end Virtual Machines to realize seamless migration of services and adjust the Virtual Machines quantity freely according to business scale and load. The user will not be aware of such operations.\"},{\"proGood\":\"Low Cost\",\"proName\":\"No hardware needs to be purchased and the billing method can be selected based on workloads, thus significantly reducing the costs for hardware with free O&M.\"},{\"proGood\":\"High Security\",\"proName\":\"EIP-based DDoS protection for Business Security.\"},{\"proGood\":\"Easy Maintenance\",\"proName\":\"The simple setting is made to achieve the strong and stable services of the Load Balancer, improve the capabilities of external services of workloads and realize easy operation, safety and reliability.\"},{\"proGood\":\"High Availability\",\"proName\":\"Resources are subject to automatic redundancy configuration and resources are deployed in the multiple availability zone so as to ensure high availability of services.\"}]",
